===Notes===
The ratio of food to prayer potions can differ significantly depending on the choice of weapons used. With:
*[[Eldritch nightmare staff]]'s special attack for prayer restoration, very few to no prayer potions need to be brought 
*The [[Toxic blowpipe]] special attack for health restoration, much more prayer potions can be brought as the heal from the special attack is still fairly strong and limits the need for additional food.

